    "Description": "We've got a shipment of contraband that needs to be hauled to a couple of different places. If you like creds, head to <EM4>~mission(Location|Address)</EM4>, load everything up, and bring it to these drop points:  \n\nDROP OFF LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)\n\n~mission(SingleToMultiToken)\n\nYou're gonna need a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> to move the boxes and enough room in your cargo hold for size <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize)</EM4> containers. \n\nAvoid other ships if you can. Security will bust you if they figure out what you're hauling, and raiders will just take it for themselves. \n\n-Twitch",
